venue.name: Pruett's House

item.description:
Come and celebrate the Winter Solstice with fellow members of the Rhode Island Atheist Society!

Please bring a dish to share (and note what you are bringing when you RSVP). I'll have plenty of beverages (adult and otherwise) and dessert for everyone.

I'll send out my address to participants a few days prior to the event. Please let me know if you have any questions. Hope to see you there!
item.name: Rhode Island Atheist Society - Winter Solstice Party
